
 get : serial_put a RS232 program of the Laboratory of Mechanics in Lille (LML), it is intended to receive a message through the serial cable from a RS232 device, it uses different GNU libraries (see --info option)

 usage: ./get --message "*IDN?"
        ./put --message "CONF:GAIN 5"
        ./get --message "READ:GAIN?"
